Skills.Name: Graceful Show Up
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by {0}% of ATK. Further raises DEF by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s. Raises DMG Received for all enemies by {2}% for 10s. Further lowers CRIT DEF by {3}% for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP, raises DEF of all allies. Raises DMG Received, lowers CRIT DEF of all enemies

Skills.Name: Gorgeous Jackpot
Skills.Description: Inflicts <code=400,param=202><color=#3398f1>Stun</color> on single enemy with highest ATK for 3s. Further inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color> + <color=red>{3}%</color>). Raises Speed of all allies by <color=red>{4}%</color> for 15s. Also raises DMG Inflicted by <color=red>{5}%</color> for 15s. Further raises ATK by {6}% for 15s if Therianthrope.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Stun and 3-hit DMG on single enemy. Raises Speed and DMG Inflicted for all allies, raises ATK if Therianthrope

Skills.Name: How About a Magic Show?
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Also reduces DMG Received by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s. Also cancels 3x Debuff effects. Further raises CRIT Rate by {3}% for 15s and CRIT ATK by {4}% for 15s if Therianthrope.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP, reduces DMG Received and cancels Debuff effect(s) of all allies, raises CRIT Rate and CRIT ATK if Therianthrope

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>5.00%-50.00%</color> according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Feverish Fortune
Skills.Description: At start of Wave, raises DMG Inflicted for all Green Elemental allies by <color=red>{1}%</color> multiplied by number of Therianthropes in party for 60s. Further raises Speed by <color=red>{4}%</color> multiplied by number of Therianthropes in party for 60s.
Skills.ShortDescription: At start of Wave, raises DMG Inflicted and Speed of all Green Elemental allies based on number of Therianthropes in party
